item.title: Teaching
item.description: I got the opportunity to work as TA for some of the best instructors of CS department, both at Purdue University and Texas A&M University. I was TA for several undergraduate Computer Science classes where I have met and helped many wonderful students. Purdue University CS 101: Digital Literacy Sessions: Fall'21, Spring'22, Fall'22, Spring'23 (Head TA), Fall'23 (Head TA), Spring'24 Instructors: Dr. George Adams & Xiaojin Liu CS 448: Introduction to Relational Database Management Systems Session: Spring'21 Instructor: Dr.
